<A NAME="chapterMinkowskiSum3Ref"></A><h1>3D Minkowski sum of Polyhedra<BR>
<I>Reference&nbsp;Manual</I></h1>

 
<p class="subtitle">Peter Hachenberger</p>
<P>

The function <I>minkowski_sum_3</I> computes the Minkowski sum of two
given 3D Nef polyhedra.
<P>

